Row names of a ClusterSet object. row_names

Source: R/ClusterSet_class.R
row_names-ClusterSet-method.Rd

The row names of a ClusterSet object.

# S4 method for class 'ClusterSet'
row_names(x)

Arguments

x

The ClusterSet object
